OL,6,FA hockey coach who claimed his
OL,7,Finterior designer wife had stabbed
OL,8,Fherself to death has been found guilty
OL,9,Fof her murder.
OL,11,FMohamed Samak, 43, denied murdering
OL,12,FJoanne Samak, 49, claiming he woke up
OL,13,Fat around 3am on July 1 last year to
OL,14,Fsee her stabbing herself at their home
OL,15,Fin Chestnut Spinney, Droitwich Spa.
