OL,3,CHockey coach who claimed wife stabbed
OL,4,Cherself found guilty of her murder
OL,6,FProsecutors said Samak, a former
OL,7,FEgyptian international hockey player
OL,8,Fand coach who worked with the Wales
OL,9,Funder-18s team, killed his wife
OL,10,Fbecause he was suffering financial
OL,11,Fproblems and had become interested in
OL,12,Fanother woman.
OL,14,FSamak told the trial his wife took her
OL,15,Fown life and was struggling with
OL,16,Falcohol and mental health problems,
OL,17,Falthough friends and family said they
OL,18,Fhad no concerns about her drinking or
OL,19,Fher mental state and that she had
OL,20,Fthings to look forward to.
