OL,6,FJoanne, who was the main breadwinner
OL,7,Fwhile Samak struggled to find a
OL,8,Fpermanent job, suffered six stab
OL,9,Fwounds to the chest and abdomen,
OL,10,Franging between 2.5cm and 10cm deep.
OL,12,FMedical experts told the jury
OL,13,Fconsiderable force was needed to
OL,14,Fpenetrate her breastbone, making it
OL,15,Fhighly unlikely she could have
OL,16,Finflicted the injury on herself.
