OL,6,FThe trial heard the couple met in 2011
OL,7,Fwhen Joanne stayed at the hotel in
OL,8,FTaba, Egypt, where Samak worked in
OL,9,Fentertainment and would make regular
OL,10,Ftrips to see each other before they
OL,11,Fmarried in 2014 and settled together
OL,12,Fin Worcestershire.
OL,14,FThe pair had suffered issues in their
OL,15,F10-year marriage and slept in separate
OL,16,Fbedrooms, with Samak claiming he
OL,17,Fmissed the "romance" in their
OL,18,Frelationship and that the pair were
OL,19,Fleading almost separate lives.
