OL,6,FSamak had admitted he had rekindled
OL,7,Fcontact with a woman from France who
OL,8,Fhe had met in 2009 and the pair had
OL,9,Fmet up in London and had kissed,
OL,10,Falthough Samak had not told his wife.
OL,12,FJoanne had also confided in a friend
OL,13,Fthat she did not love her husband and
OL,14,Fwished she could divorce him.
OL,16,FDescribing the events of the night
OL,17,FJoanne died, Samak told the jury he
OL,18,Fwas woken up by a scream from his wife
OL,19,Fand went out on to the landing at
OL,20,Ftheir home to see her in the corner
OL,21,Fstabbing herself.
