OL,6,FBut when he called the emergency
OL,7,Fservices at 4.10am, more than an hour
OL,8,Fafter the incident, he told the call
OL,9,Fhandler he had gone to the bathroom
OL,10,Fand decided to check on his wife, who
OL,11,Fslept in a separate bedroom, and found
OL,12,Fher slumped on the bed with a knife in
OL,13,Fher stomach.
OL,15,FHe told the trial he had lied at first
OL,16,Fbecause he panicked and feared he
OL,17,Fwould be blamed for her injuries.
