OL,6,FSamak said he was in shock and crying
OL,7,Fon the floor after the incident and
OL,8,Fwhen he finally called 999, the call
OL,9,Fhandler told him to start CPR but he
OL,10,Fadmitted he did not, despite being
OL,11,Ftrained in the procedure and having a
OL,12,Ffirst aid kit in his bedroom.
OL,14,FThe court heard Joanne's blood was
OL,15,Falso found on clothing Samak had
OL,16,Fhidden in the loft.
