OL,6,FJonathan Roe, from the Crown
OL,7,FProsecution Service, said: "Mohamed
OL,8,FSamak killed his wife and tried to
OL,9,Fclaim she had taken her own life,
OL,10,Frepeatedly lying to police to avoid
OL,11,Fresponsibility.
OL,13,F"This callous attempt to present his
OL,14,Fcrime as a suicide has caused further
OL,15,Fanguish to Jo's family.
