OL,6,FThey said: "Jo was a beautiful,
OL,7,Fthoughtful person. She was loyal, kind
OL,8,Fand caring to everyone that touched
OL,9,Fher life. She was deeply loved by us,
OL,10,Fher family and her many, many friends.
OL,12,F"Most importantly, she was an amazing
OL,13,Fmummy. Her loss has had a devastating
OL,14,Fimpact on everyone who knew and loved
OL,15,Fher, and we will never come to terms
OL,16,Fwith losing her in such a cruel and
OL,17,Fsenseless way.
