OL,6,F"Jo's zest for life was infectious.
OL,7,FShe was generous, creative and full of
OL,8,Ffun, with a wonderful sense of style
OL,9,Fand a passion for interior design,
OL,10,Ffashion, art and nature.
OL,12,F"Jo had so much more life to live, and
OL,13,Fwe will miss her and love her forever".
OL,15,FAfter a retrial at Worcester Crown
OL,16,FCourt, Samak was found guilty by a
OL,17,Fjury on Wednesday afternoon, the Crown
OL,18,FProsecution Service said.
